column2: Recursively assigning properties on objects may cause accidental modification of a built-in prototype object.
column4: The property chain [["part"|"relative:///dist/utils/object/set.js:5:23:5:26"]] is recursively assigned to [["objectRef"|"relative:///dist/utils/object/set.js:14:5:14:13"]] without guarding against prototype pollution.
